commands_raw:
A new face doth graze this great tower? 
Curious it be, thou of seemingly desperate nature. 
I see thine clothing be of low quality, could be it riches thou seek? 
Answer mine question, as I be The First of Power.
What doth thou wish to gain from thine expedition?

?> You were right, I’m here for the riches! -> No-Run-First-Choice-One
?> I seek a purpose -> No-Run-First-Choice-Two
?> HOLY SMOKES A TALKING PILE OF ROCKS! -> No-Run-First-Choice-Three
?> What’s it to ya, stone-face? -> No-Run-First-Choice-Four
?> I don’t know… maybe I’ll get something out of it… -> No-Run-First-Choice-Five
